{
  "texts": [
    "Our UDA accuracy of 68.63% significantly outperforms the \"Source Only's\" accuracy of 61.80%.",
    "On the other hand, the improvement in the DG setting is not so significant, with an accuracy of 62.64%.",
    "However, even in this setting, we observe a potential for softening the domain shift and achieve better performance.",
    "It is worth noting that, on our settings, our method outperforms the other UDA methods used for comparison.",
    "Among the UDA baselines, MMD achieves the highest accuracy of 65.58%, which is 3.05% less than our method."
  ]
}